# Code Owners for DEV 110 Course Repository

# This file defines who must review and approve changes to different parts of the repository

# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo
# All PRs require approval from @ZakBrinlee
* @ZakBrinlee

# Root files require instructor approval
/*.* @ZakBrinlee
/*.md @ZakBrinlee
/*.sln @ZakBrinlee

# GitHub configuration requires instructor approval
/.github/ @ZakBrinlee

# Workflow files require instructor approval
/.github/workflows/ @ZakBrinlee

# Documentation requires instructor approval
/docs/ @ZakBrinlee

# Module README files require instructor approval
**/README.md @ZakBrinlee

# Test files require instructor approval
**/tests/ @ZakBrinlee

# Solution files require instructor approval
**/solution/ @ZakBrinlee

# Students can freely edit their starter code, .gitignore, and .vscode
# (These are not protected by the above rules)
